<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 14:09:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际法院：以色列占领巴勒斯坦领土是“事实上的吞并”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-live/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-of-west-bank-east-jerusalem/00000190-cade-dfb6-afbe-effe53000000</link><description>尽管联合国最高法院的咨询意见不具有约束力，但针对以色列的裁决可能会导致国际社会对定居点运动实施更严厉的制裁</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 12:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-live/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-of-west-bank-east-jerusalem/00000190-cade-dfb6-afbe-effe53000000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列幸福指数排名高是一个弥天大谎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-israels-high-ranking-on-the-happiness-index-is-one-big-lie/00000190-c93b-dfb6-afbe-ef7baaca0000</link><description>以色列在国际幸福指数中的高排名掩盖了一个正在遭受希望丧失和冷漠的社会。要改变这种情况，我们必须培养一种不同的感觉：愤怒</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:51:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-israels-high-ranking-on-the-happiness-index-is-one-big-lie/00000190-c93b-dfb6-afbe-ef7baaca0000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装无人机对特拉维夫的致命袭击标志着自 10 月 7 日以来战争进入戏剧性的新阶段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/houthi-drone-strike-on-tel-aviv-marks-a-new-phase-in-the-october-7-war/00000190-ca69-db81-a3f7-fafd3dbf0000</link><description>胡塞武装配备了伊朗提供的日益先进的远程武器，他们表示特拉维夫现在将成为主要目标。这意味着以色列的多线战争变得更加激烈，而且冲突将演变成区域性的</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:51:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/houthi-drone-strike-on-tel-aviv-marks-a-new-phase-in-the-october-7-war/00000190-ca69-db81-a3f7-fafd3dbf0000</guid></item><item><title>网络中断导致航班停飞，给以色列和世界各地造成干扰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-health-ministry-says-global-outage-causing-hospital-services-to-malfunction/00000190-c9cf-d3e0-a5fd-ebffe5480000</link><description>以色列卫生部表示，医院和其他卫生服务机构受到影响</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-health-ministry-says-global-outage-causing-hospital-services-to-malfunction/00000190-c9cf-d3e0-a5fd-ebffe5480000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫无人机袭击造成 1 人死亡、8 人受伤；胡塞武装宣称对此事负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-eight-wounded-in-drone-attack-on-tel-aviv-houthis-claim-responsibility/00000190-c991-d3e0-a5fd-ebb55bbe0000</link><description>无人机爆炸造成八人受伤 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它识别出了这架无人机，但由于人为错误，没有拦截或激活警报器</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 06:52:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-eight-wounded-in-drone-attack-on-tel-aviv-houthis-claim-responsibility/00000190-c991-d3e0-a5fd-ebb55bbe0000</guid></item><item><title>“就连我当地的犹太社区现在也不支持以色列了。很难消化’</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-19/ty-article/.highlight/even-my-local-jewish-community-doesnt-stand-with-israel-now-its-hard-to-digest/00000190-c91b-d3e0-a5fd-ebbffe310000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名犹太裔美国人在经历加沙战争后的反犹太复国主义和反犹太主义后考虑搬到以色列，而一名以色列医生则搬到荷兰，以便可以行医并过上自己的生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 04:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-19/ty-article/.highlight/even-my-local-jewish-community-doesnt-stand-with-israel-now-its-hard-to-digest/00000190-c91b-d3e0-a5fd-ebbffe310000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普发誓要“结束因袭击以色列而引发的战争”，并指责拜登10月7日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/u