0-c748-d258-a3ff-e7c9be560000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡将与被扣押在加沙的以色列人质的一些亲属一起进入国会，他们希望利用这个机会倡导达成协议。其他人会在外面抗议，指责总理阻碍谈判并利用他们的困境来实现他的个人目标</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/in-washington-visit-netanyahu-will-once-again-spark-division-among-hostages-families/00000190-c748-d258-a3ff-e7c9be560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军发言人表示，越来越多的迹象表明哈马斯领导人穆罕默德·德伊夫在以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-live/idf-says-checking-possible-drone-attack-after-several-injured-in-tel-aviv-blast/00000190-c8c3-dfb6-afbe-efe376560000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，自早上以来，黎巴嫩向以色列发射了 65 枚火箭弹和无人机 ■ 胡塞武装声称对特拉维夫袭击事件负责 ■ 以色列国防军表示，无人机并未被拦截，也没有由于人为失误而启动警报器 ■ 以色列陆军发言人表示，越来越多的证据表明哈马斯的德伊夫被杀以色列罢工 ■ 计算机系统导致以色列医院中断 ■ 德国外长呼吁加沙停火，称以色列国防军“一次又一次”袭击安全区</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:24:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-live/idf-says-checking-possible-drone-attack-after-several-injured-in-tel-aviv-blast/00000190-c8c3-dfb6-afbe-efe376560000</guid></item><item><title>当一名极端正统派定居者提出向一名极端世俗的特拉维夫人传授犹太教时，发生了什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-an-haredi-settler-offered-to-teach-an-ultra-secular-tel-avivian-about-judaism/00000190-c7d8-dfb6-afbe-effaf8a20000</link><description>有一天，有人敲我的门。那是一个极端正统派的人，微笑着问我是否想学习犹太教。我邀请他进来</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 23:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-an-haredi-settler-offered-to-teach-an-ultra-secular-tel-avivian-about-judaism/00000190-c7d8-dfb6-afbe-effaf8a20000</guid></item><item><title>迈克·约翰逊威胁要逮捕扰乱内塔尼亚胡国会演讲的议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/this-is-an-attack-on-americans-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-appeal-to-republicans/00000190-c7d0-dbfd-a594-c7f76fbf0001</link><description>在共和党大会间隙的“向亲以色列民选官员致敬”上，约翰逊议长告诉共和党犹太人：我们是唯一亲以色列的政党</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 22:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/this-is-an-attack-on-americans-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-appeal-to-republicans/00000190-c7d0-dbfd-a594-c7f76fbf0001</guid></item><item><title>在 10 月 7 日之后的世界中，犹太人不再有应许之地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-the-post-october-7-world-there-are-no-promised-lands-for-jews/00000190-c6aa-d3e0-a5fd-efbf138a0000</link><description>去年对犹太人来说是非常不安的一年，他们感觉一段独特的宽容和安全时期可能已经结束。这不仅是哈马斯的袭击，也是以色列内部政治的事态发展</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 21:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-the-post-october-7-world-there-are-no-promised-lands-for-jews/00000190-c6aa-d3e0-a5fd-efbf138a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极端主义政府煽动对人质的仇恨，并产生了后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-extremist-government-is-stoking-hate-against-hostages-and-there-are-consequences/00000190-c67d-de8b-adfc-df7da0bb0000</link><description>一小部分但直言不讳的以色列选民在极端主义领导人的鼓励下，猛烈抨击人质亲属在试图确保加沙被囚禁的亲人获释时所做的斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:55:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-extremist-government-is-stoking-hate-against-hostages-and-there-are-consequences/00000190-c67d-de8b-adfc-df7da0bb0000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列实施武器禁运？承认巴勒斯坦吗？英国新政府即将做出的政策决定承诺“为善的力量”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/arms-embargo-on-israel-recognize-palestine-looming-policy-decisions-for-new-u-k-govt/00000190-c65a-dbfd-a594-c67fd2860000</link><description>包括外交大臣戴维·拉米在内的新英国工党政府无意卷入关于以色列和加沙的两极分化和政治有毒的政策辩论，而是更愿意在制裁暴力的约旦河西岸定居者等问题上保持共识。但正如一位专家指出的那样：“你永远无法逃避以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/arms-embargo-on-israel-recognize-palestine-looming-policy-decisions-for-new-u-k-govt/00000190-c65a-dbfd-a594-c67fd2860000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院将裁定以色列占领约旦河西岸是否非法：为什么是现在以及以色列和巴勒斯坦人将如何反应？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-why-now-and-what-will-be-the-reactions/00000190-c5ba-dbfd-a594-c5bfc8e70000</link><description>海牙最新的历史性判决：国际法院的程序与国际刑事法院有何不同？ ■ 以色列是否配合听证会？ ■ 如果法院裁定以色列对约旦河西岸和东耶路撒冷的占领非法，会产生什么影响？</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-why-now-and-what-will-be-the-reactions/00000190-c5ba-dbfd-a594-c5bfc8e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院强调任命最高法院院长的紧迫性，呼吁双方在8月8日前达成妥协</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/top-court-stresses-urgency-of-appointing-court-president-calls-on-sides-to-compromise/00000190-c6dc-db81-a3f7-f6dc488a0000</link><description>法官们在请愿书听证会上发表讲话，该请愿书要求司法政变策划者司法部长亚里夫·莱文(Yariv Levin)任命常任法院院长。 “任命最高法院院长的必要性还有疑问吗？”奥弗·格罗斯科普夫法官表示</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:25:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/top-court-stresses-urgency-of-appointing-court-president-calls-on-sides-to-compromise/00000190-c6dc-db81-a3f7-f6dc488a0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 286 天：以色列议会投票反对建立巴勒斯坦国的原则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-286-knesset-voted-against-principle-of-establishing-palestinian-state/00000190-c6cc-d966-abf0-e6ec03820000</link><description>以色列议会投票反对建立巴勒斯坦国的原则 ■ 极端正统沙斯党呼吁内塔尼亚胡敲定人质协议 ■ 失去亲人的以色列家庭表示，他们正在组织建立一个民事调查委员会，在没有国家委员会的情况下 ■ 以色列人在西部被弹片炸伤银行汽车爆炸 ■ 战争进入 286 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 17:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-286-knesset-voted-against-principle-of-establishing-palestinian-state/00000190-c6cc-d966-abf0-e6ec03820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级警官在被拍摄暴力逮捕反政府抗议者后被免除指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/top-police-officer-cleared-of-charges-after-being-filmed-violently-arresting-protester/00000190-c669-d2f8-abdb-e66dbb380000</link><description>周四早些时候，警察调查部门起诉了去年 3 月特拉维夫向反政府示威者投掷眩晕手榴弹的五名警察。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 16:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/top-police-officer-cleared-of-charges-after-being-filmed-violently-arresting-protester/00000190-c669-d2f8-abdb-e66dbb380000</guid></item></channel></rss>